{
  "stem": "9730.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I, I mean, our team was made up of a captain, a lieutenant, a master sergeant, a tech sergeant, and some other sergeants.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, we-- working together closely, we, we did become quite friendly, although there were some shifts in personnel as time went along, and some of them dropped out and replacements came in.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But also, with the unit that we were attached to, we really became quite friendly with some of the people that we got to know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] especially the regimental headquarters staff.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] throughout my entire Army experience, I personally did not [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] come across any overt anti-Semitism, as some people have said they did.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were a few.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, members of, of my intelligence team were, you know, were of course-- most of them were from Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this sometimes led to some rather peculiar and even funny incidents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, when we-- the same type of personnel also made up the teams on maneuvers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when, when we first encountered some of the troops, here we were, some of-- with some of these personnels speaking with heavy German accents.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the time, the troops absolutely didn't know what to make of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- on--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on, especially during the Battle of the Bulge much later, some, some of our personnel had quite a bit of, quite some problems identifying themselves as, as American troops and, and being believed by the guards, you know, when asked for the password.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, well, we sometimes, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we sometimes would play some, some games.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
